Subject: [PATCH 5/6] drm/panel: add motorola perry Ofilm 499v0 panel

Hand-converted from downstream MDSS DTSI
(kernel/motorola/msm8953 dsi-panel-mot-ofilm-499-720p-video-common.dtsi,
node qcom,mdss_dsi_mot_ofilm_499_720p_video_v0) following the lmdpdg
output style of panel-drivers#6, using the mipi_dsi_multi_context API.
Timings are identical to the Tianma 499 variants; only the DCS init
sequence differs (Novatek-style CMD2 pages vs Ilitek ILI9881 on Tianma).
Compatible: motorola,perry-499v0-ofilm

